metadata.name: London in 2042
metadata.description:
287f 3820x2160 1.94GB .mov  

Imagining London in two decades, having more organic shaped buildings with green spaces, suspended gardens with aquaponics, noiseless transportation in 3d space and renewable energy production. This is the longest personal project that I made to date and a short breakdown of it is posted on my twitter; also, please DM me for the highest quality video in 4k after purchase.
